Correlations for Mean Outcome Measures vs NARA

corr_ct <- cor.test(mean_data$Total_Time, mean_data$NARA, method = "spearman")
corr_ct
## 
##  Spearman's rank correlation rho
## 
## data:  mean_data$Total_Time and mean_data$NARA
## S = 4919, p-value = 0.0001256
## alternative hypothesis: true rho is not equal to 0
## sample estimates:
##        rho 
## -0.6817178
